data.description:
Situated on a corner lot, 3 bedrooms and 1.5 bathrooms. The layout is ideal for a growing family. Hardwood floors throughout the main living areas, the house exudes warmth and character. Standout features of this home is the oversized two-car garage. It provides ample storage space.  You'll never have to worry about battling the elements or carrying groceries through the rain again! 
The lower level of the house includes a recreation room, perfect for entertaining or simply enjoying quality time with family and friends. The built-in bar adds a touch of sophistication to the space, making it an ideal spot for hosting memorable gatherings. This home also offers a beautifully fenced in yard, providing a serene outdoor oasis where you can relax and unwind after a long day.
